neverovatnog automobila, g. Arav Kapura!

422
00:40:38,253 --> 00:40:39,845
Velika ruka!

423
00:40:46,928 --> 00:40:53,026
Moji dragi prijatelji, do sada sam bio
samo delio moj proizvod sa vama.

424
00:40:54,368 --> 00:40:58,961
